%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20reckons%20with%20his%20third%20assassination%20attempt%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223320%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22First%20Lady%20Melania%20Trump%20and%20U.S.%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20attend%20the%20annual%20White%20House%20Correspondents%20Association%20Dinner%20April%2025%2C%202026%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC.%20The%20president%20is%20making%20his%20first%20appearance%20at%20the%20event%20which%20he%20has%20shunned%20in%20the%20past.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69eea9c63fecbb42897a4435%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20at%20the%20White%20House%20Correspondents%20Association%20Dinner.%3Cp%3ENathan%20Howard%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETrump%20spoke%20to%20%26quot%3B60%20Minutes%26quot%3B%20on%20Sunday%2C%20after%20the%20White%20House%20Correspondents'%20Dinner%20shooting%20on%20Saturday%20night.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDuring%20the%20interview%2C%20the%20president%20was%20asked%20about%20the%20accused%20gunman's%20motives.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETrump%20said%20none%20of%20the%20accusations%20in%20a%20written%20manifesto%20had%20anything%20to%20do%20with%20him.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20reckoned%20with%20the%20string%20of%20assassination%20attempts%20he%20has%20faced%20this%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20an%20interview%20with%20CBS's%20%26quot%3B60%20Minutes%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20he%20had%20read%20a%20manifesto%20written%20by%20the%20gunman%20who%20entered%20the%20annual%20press%20dinner%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20on%20Saturday%20and%20was%20quickly%20subdued%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20radicalized.%20He%20was%20a%20Christian%20%E2%80%94%20a%20believer%2C%20and%20then%20he%20became%20an%20anti-Christian%2C%20and%20he%20had%20a%20lotta%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20president%20pushed%20back%20when%20%26quot%3B60%20Minutes%26quot%3B%20host%20Norah%20O'Donnell%20read%20a%20line%20from%20the%20manifesto%20that%20called%20Trump%20a%20pedophile%20and%20a%20rapist%2C%20among%20other%20accusations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3EI'm%20not%20a%20pedophile.%20You%20read%20that%20crap%20from%20some%20sick%20person%3F%20I%20got%20associated%20with%20all%20%E2%80%94%20stuff%20that%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20me.%20I%20was%20totally%20exonerated%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20he%20wasn't%20involved%20with%20%26quot%3BEpstein%20or%20other%20things%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20referring%20to%20the%20disgraced%20financier%20and%20convicted%20sex%20offender%2C%20Jeffrey%20Epstein.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20said%20he%20thought%20part%20of%20the%20reason%20he%20was%20facing%20threats%20stems%20from%20anti-Trump%20rhetoric%20and%20demonstrations%20like%20the%20%26quot%3BNo%20Kings%26quot%3B%20protests%2C%20a%20series%20of%20rallies%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20reason%20you%20have%20people%20like%20that%20is%20you%20have%20people%20doing%20No%20Kings.%20I'm%20not%20a%20king.%20What%20I%20am%20%E2%80%94%20if%20I%20was%20a%20king%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20be%20dealing%20with%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20O'Donnell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20political%20violence%20has%20gone%20back%20hundreds%20of%20years%2C%20echoing%20comments%20from%20his%20Saturday%20night%20press%20conference%20that%20all%20countries%20face%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20assassinated.%20People%20are%20injured.%20People%20are%20hurt.%20And%20I'm%20not%20sure%20that%20it's%20any%20more%20now%20than%20there%20was%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20on%20%26quot%3B60%20Minutes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20press%20conference%20on%20Saturday%20night%2C%20Trump%20said%20being%20a%20president%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20dangerous%20profession%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20facing%20the%20threat%20of%20political%20violence%20is%20%26quot%3Bpart%20of%20the%20job.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%208%3A36%20p.m.%20on%20Saturday%20night%2C%20shots%20were%20fired%20outside%20the%20ballroom%20of%20the%20Washington%20Hilton%2C%20where%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fattendee-describes-low-security-at-white-house-correspondents-dinner-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EWhite%20House%20Correspondents'%20Dinner%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20underway.%20It%20marked%20the%20third%20time%20in%20three%20years%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-evacuated-from-white-house-correspondents-dinner-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20faced%20the%20threat%20of%20assassination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20have%20not%20yet%20publicly%20identified%20the%20suspect.%20However%2C%20photos%20of%20the%20White%20House%20Correspondents'%20Dinner%20shooter%20posted%20online%20by%20Trump%20on%20Saturday%20night%20matched%20a%20LinkedIn%20profile%20belonging%20to%20Cole%20Allen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMultiple%20outlets%2C%20including%20the%20Associated%20Press%2C%20have%20also%20reported%20that%20Allen%20is%20the%20suspect%20in%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAllen%2C%2031%2C%20is%20listed%20as%20a%20resident%20of%20Torrance%2C%20California.%20Police%20conducted%20an%20overnight%20raid%20at%20an%20address%20in%20the%20state%20linked%20to%20Allen%20in%20an%20online%20database.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20LinkedIn%20describes%20him%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bmechanical%20engineer%20and%20computer%20scientist%20by%20degree%2C%20independent%20game%20developer%20by%20experience%2C%20teacher%20by%20birth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EActing%20US%20Attorney%20General%20Todd%20Blanche%20said%20Sunday%20in%20several%20TV%20news%20interviews%20that%20the%20shooter%20left%20a%20manifesto%2C%20in%20which%20he%20said%20he%20intended%20to%20target%20Trump%20administration%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20know%20that%20there%20were%20some%20writings%2C%20and%20we've%20already%20spoken%20with%20several%20witnesses%20who%20knew%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20NBC%20News'%20%26quot%3BMeet%20the%20Press.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlanche%20said%20the%20suspect%20traveled%20from%20Los%20Angeles%20to%20Washington%20by%20train%20and%20checked%20into%20the%20hotel%20where%20the%20event%20was%20held%20with%20two%20guns%20and%20a%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJeanine%20Pirro%2C%20the%20US%20Attorney%20for%20the%20District%20of%20Columbia%2C%20said%20the%20defendant%20has%20been%20charged%20with%20two%20counts%20of%20using%20a%20firearm%20during%20a%20crime%20of%20violence%20and%20one%20count%20of%20assault%20on%20a%20law%20enforcement%20officer%20using%20a%20dangerous%20weapon.%20He%20will%20be%20arraigned%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-white-house-correspondents-dinner-shooting-interview-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777251200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69eea9dda98bc8fdc096ef9a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-white-house-correspondents-dinner-shooting-interview-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Trump%2C%20on%20%26quot%3B60%20Minutes%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20he%20had%20read%20the%20accused%20gunman's%20manifesto.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cteh%40businessinsider.com%20(Cheryl%20Teh%2CLakshmi%20Varanasi)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Iranians%20can%20call%20us%20but%20they%20must%20agree%20to%20no%20nukes%2C%20else%20no%20point%20in%20meeting%3A%20Trump%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777249835000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-1305414