20Hormuz%20remains%20closed%2C%20and%20the%20US%20Navy%20continues%20to%20blockade%20Iran's%20ports.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20price%20of%20oil%20inched%20upward%20on%20Sunday%20as%20a%20second%20round%20of%20peace%20talks%20between%20the%20US%20and%20Iran%20never%20materialized.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrent%20crude%20oil%20futures%20rose%20nearly%202%25%20to%20%24101.07%20a%20barrel%20when%20the%20markets%20opened%20at%206%20p.m.%20in%20New%20York.%20West%20Texas%20Intermediate%20inched%20up%20by%20around%201%25%20to%20reach%20%2495.57%20a%20barrel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20end%20to%20the%20conflict%2C%20which%20has%20lasted%20nearly%20two%20months%2C%20remained%20uncertain%20this%20weekend.%20White%20House%20press%20secretary%20Karoline%20Leavitt%20said%20Special%20Envoys%20Steve%20Witkoff%20and%20Jared%20Kushner%20would%20travel%20to%20Islamabad%20for%20negotiations%20during%20a%20press%20briefing%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20an%20X%20post%20by%20Iran's%20Ministry%20of%20Foreign%20Affairs%20on%20Friday%20said%20no%20meeting%20was%20scheduled%20between%20the%20US%20and%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20on%20Saturday%2C%20an%20Iranian%20delegation%20left%20Pakistan%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20he%20would%20cancel%20Witkoff's%20and%20Kushner's%20trip.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20no%20new%20round%20of%20talks%20was%20held.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20cancelled%20the%20trip%20of%20my%20representatives%20going%20to%20Islamabad%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20to%20meet%20with%20the%20Iranians.%20Too%20much%20time%20wasted%20on%20traveling%2C%20too%20much%20work!%26quot%3B%20Trump%20wrote%20in%20a%20Truth%20Social%20post%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BAlso%2C%20we%20have%20all%20the%20cards%2C%20they%20have%20none!%20If%20they%20want%20to%20talk%2C%20all%20they%20have%20to%20do%20is%20call!!!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVice%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fwhat-smart-people-saying-failed-us-iran-peace-talks-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJD%20Vance%3C%2Fa%3E%20traveled%20to%20Pakistan%20on%20April%2011%20to%20negotiate%20with%20Iran%2C%20though%20those%20talks%20ultimately%20failed%20after%2021%20hours.%20On%20April%2019%2C%20Trump%20said%20negotiations%20with%20Iran%20would%20resume%20that%20week%2C%20but%20hours%20later%2C%20Iran's%20official%20news%20agency%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpresident-donald-trump-iran-peace-talks-hormuz-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eit%20would%20not%20participate%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20failed%20talks%2C%20the%20US%20and%20Iran%20have%20so%20far%20held%20to%20a%20ceasefire.%20Trump%20said%20he%20extended%20the%20ceasefire%20in%20a%20Truth%20Social%20post%20on%20April%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20peace%20talks%20between%20the%20US%20and%20Iran%20remain%20elusive%2C%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%20%E2%80%94%20a%20waterway%20off%20Iran's%20coast%20through%20which%20a%20fifth%20of%20the%20globe's%20oil%20and%20liquefied%20natural%20gas%20passes%20%E2%80%94%20has%20remained%20closed.%20Iran%20initially%20closed%20the%20strait%20in%20late%20February%20following%20the%20US%20and%20Israel's%20attacks%2C%20but%20briefly%20reopened%20it%20in%20April%20as%20part%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-smart-people-saying-about-donald-trump-ceasefire-deal-iran-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eceasefire%20deal%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20after%20the%20first%20round%20of%20failed%20peace%20talks%20in%20Islamabad%2C%20Trump%20announced%20the%20US%20would%20implement%20a%20naval%20blockade%20of%20Iran's%20ports.%20In%20response%2C%20Iran%20again%20closed%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20closure%2C%20compounded%20by%20damage%20to%2