%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20shooting%20took%20place%20at%20the%20White%20House%20Correspondents'%20Dinner%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20said%20the%20incident%20underscored%20the%20need%20to%20build%20his%20White%20House%20ballroom.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20judge%20halted%20Trump's%20ballroom%20renovations%20in%20March%2C%20saying%20he%20lacked%20legal%20authority.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20hours%20after%20a%20shooting%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhitlon-hotel-washington-shooting-witness-white-house-correspondents-dinner-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhite%20House%20Correspondents'%20Dinner%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Saturday%2C%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20tried%20to%20rally%20support%20for%20his%20new%20White%20House%20ballroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20event%20would%20never%20have%20happened%20with%20the%20Militarily%20Top%20Secret%20Ballroom%20currently%20under%20construction%20at%20the%20White%20House%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20on%20Truth%20Social%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Trump%20administration%20first%20announced%20plans%20to%20build%20a%2090%2C000-square-foot%20ballroom%20in%20place%20of%20the%20White%20House's%20East%20Wing%20in%20July%202025.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20the%20White%20House%20said%20the%20ballroom%20would%20allow%20officials%20to%20host%20large-scale%20events%20with%20world%20leaders%20without%20using%20an%20%26quot%3Bunsightly%26quot%3B%20tent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20president%20said%20the%20ballroom%20would%20cost%20about%20%24400%20million%2C%20which%20he%20planned%20to%20raise%20from%20wealthy%20donors.%20Some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-white-house-ballroom-donors-list-apple-meta-amazon-microsoft-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emajor%20US%20companies%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20Amazon%2C%20Meta%2C%20and%20Apple%20%E2%80%94%20have%20already%20offered%20to%20help%20fund%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConstruction%20began%20with%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20East%20Wing%20in%20October%2C%20but%20has%20since%20been%20held%20up%20by%20the%20courts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Trust%20for%20Historic%20Preservation%20of%20the%20United%20States%2C%20chartered%20by%20Congress%20in%201949%2C%20filed%20a%20lawsuit%20in%20December%20to%20stop%20construction.%20In%20a%20press%20release%2C%20the%20trust%20said%20Trump%20%26quot%3Bdisregarded%26quot%3B%20several%20laws%20and%20failed%20to%20obtain%20the%20necessary%20approval%20from%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20federal%20judge%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjudge-stops-trumps-white-house-ballroom-renovations-construction-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehalted%20construction%20of%20the%20ballroom%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20March%2C%20saying%20Trump%20lacked%20the%20legal%20authority%20to%20build%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNothing%20should%20be%20allowed%20to%20interfere%20with%20its%20construction%2C%20which%20is%20on%20budget%20and%20substantially%20ahead%20of%20schedule!!!%26quot%3B%20Trump%20wrote%20on%20Truth%20Social%20on%20Sunday%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20has%20%26quot%3Bevery%20highest%20security%20feature%20there%20is.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20senior%20members%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-evacuated-from-white-house-correspondents-dinner-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump%20administration%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20the%20president%20and%20first%20lady%20Melania%20Trump%2C%20were%20present%20at%20the%20Washington%20Hilton%20on%20Saturday%20night%20for%20the%20White%20House%20Correspondents'%20Dinner%20when%20shots%20rang%20out.%20No%20officials%20were%20injured%20in%20the%20shooting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMembers%20of%20the%20press%20present%20during%20the%20incident%20said%20they%20were%20surprised%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhitlon-hotel-washington-shooting-witness-white-house-correspondents-dinner-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20lack%20of%20security%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20venue.%20%26quot%3BOn%20my%20way%20out%2C%20I%20think%20about%20the%20security%20precautions%20%E2%80%94%20or%20lack%20thereof%20%E2%80%94%20that%20had%20struck%20me%20as%20surprisingly%20lax%20throughout%20the%20evening%2C%20given%20the%20presence%20of%20Trump%2C%20Vice%20President%20JD%20Vance%2C%20and%20several%20cabinet%20members%2C%26quot%3B%20Tim%20R%C3%B6hn%2C%20the%20senior%20editor%20of%20the%20Axel%20Springer%20Global%20Reporters%20Network%2C%20said.%20Business%20Insider%20is%20part%20of%20the%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20said%20they%20have%20a%20suspect%20in%20custody%2C%20widely%20identified%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcole-allen-shooter-white-house-correspondents-dinner-trump-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E31-year-old%20Cole%20Allen%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Torrance%2C%20California.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20interim%20chief%20of%20the%20Metropolitan%20Police%20Department%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20Jeffrey%20Carroll%2C%20said%20during%20a%20press%20conference%20that%20the%20suspect%20was%20armed%20with%20a%20shotgun%2C%20handgun%2C%20and%20knives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJeanine%20Pirro%2C%20US%20Attorney%20for%20the%20District%20of%20Columbia%2C%20said%20the%20suspect%20has%20been%20charged%20with%20one%20count%20of%20assault%20on%20a%20law%20enforcement%20officer%20using%20a%20dangerous%20weapon%20and%20two%20counts%20of%20using%20a%20firearm%20during%20a%20crime%20of%20violence.%20He%20will%20be%20arraigned%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETodd%20Blanche%2C%20acting%20US%20attorney%20general%2C%20said%20during%20a%20Sunday%20interview%20on%20NBC's%20%26quot%3BMeet%20the%20Press%26quot%3B%20that%20law%20enforcement%20believes%20the%20suspect%20was%20targeting%20members%20of%20the%20Trump%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3