thes.%20I%20heard%20employees%20say%20that%20sometimes%20there%20are%20high-ticket%20items%20like%20AirPods.%20I%20saw%20a%20lot%20of%20holiday%20items%2C%20like%20Halloween%20decorations%2C%20Christmas%20ribbon%2C%20and%20stockings.%20There%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20seasonal%20stuff%20at%20our%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20also%20a%20lot%20of%20auto%20parts.%20My%20husband%20couldn't%20figure%20out%20what%20they%20were%20at%20first%3B%20we%20had%20to%20look%20them%20up%20on%20Google.%20Another%20person%20shopping%20near%20us%20told%20us%20they%20were%20going%20to%20resell%20them%20on%20eBay%20because%20they%20were%20%2415%20here%20and%20going%20for%20%24700%20online.%20I%20think%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20were%20doing%20that.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ended%20up%20buying%20the%20tumbler%20I%20showed%20on%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freels%2FDWj2KwfD2uf%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eviral%20Instagram%20reel%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20was%20%2435%2C%20and%20I%20got%20it%20for%20%2415.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2242795234-4cd4-418d-a4a8-0e36d54de497%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI'd%20shop%20them%20again%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20the%20experience%20was%20fun.%20I'd%20shop%20again%20at%20the%20Bin%20Wins%2C%20but%20mostly%20for%20entertainment%20value%2C%20not%20actual%20deals%20on%20stuff%20my%20family%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20everything%20in%20the%20bins%20was%20worth%20%2415%2C%20but%20if%20you%20could%20find%20them%20on%20the%20%242%20day%2C%20it%20would%20be%20worth%20it.%20It%20would%20be%20a%20fun%20thing%20to%20do%20with%20someone%20%E2%80%94%20grab%20a%20coffee%20and%20go%20through%20the%20bins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstaples-bin-wins-review-amazon-returns-deals-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777234081000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69dc00