ld%2Fus%2Fdc-gunman-cole-thomas-allen-said-in-his-manifesto-that-he-would-spare-one-trump-administration-official-and-it-was-%2Famp_articleshow%2F130538143.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fdc-gunman-cole-thomas-allen-said-in-his-manifesto-that-he-would-spare-one-trump-administration-official-and-it-was-%2Famp_articleshow%2F130538143.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20New%20York%20Times%20says%20this%20is%20why%20the%20shooting%20didn't%20make%20its%20Sunday%20edition%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22861%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22NYT%20front%20page%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ee5d3ca98bc8fdc096ef3c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22646%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENews%20of%20the%20shooting%20at%20the%20White%20House%20Correspondents'%20Dinner%20on%20Saturday%20night%20happened%20too%20late%20to%20make%20the%20Sunday%20morning%20edition%20of%20The%20New%20York%20Times.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20The%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Sunday%20print%20edition%20of%20the%20Times%20made%20no%20mention%20of%20the%20White%20House%20Correspondents'%20dinner%20shooting.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20critics%20online%20called%20the%20omission%20intentional.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Times%20said%20it%20sent%20its%20Sunday%20edition%20to%20press%20at%208%20p.m.%20on%20Saturday%20night%2C%20before%20the%20shooting%20took%20place.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAt%208%3A36%20p.m.%20on%20Saturday%20night%2C%20shots%20were%20fired%20outside%20the%20ballroom%20of%20the%20Washington%20Hilton%2C%20where%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fattendee-describes-low-security-at-white-house-correspondents-dinner-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWhite%20House%20Correspondents'%20Dinner%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20well%20underway.%20It%20marked%20the%20third%20time%20in%20three%20years%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-evacuated-from-white-house-correspondents-dinner-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%20faced%20the%20threat%20of%20assassination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20news%2C%20however%2C%20did%20not%20make%20The%20New%20York%20Times'%20Sunday%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Times%20covered%20the%20shooting%20extensively%20on%20its%20website.%20For%20its%20Sunday%20print%20edition%2C%20however%2C%20the%20next%20day's%20news%20had%20already%20been%20set%20when%20the%20shooting%20occurred%2C%20setting%20it%20up%20for%20a%20backlash%20from%20its%20critics%2C%20who%20believed%20it%20was%20intentional.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20seemed%20so%20outrageous%20(even%20for%20the%20NYT)%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20verify%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Sequoia%20partner%20Shaun%20Maguire%20wrote%20on%20X%20alongside%20a%20photo%20of%20the%20Times'%20Sunday%20paper.%20%26quot%3BI%20went%20and%20got%20a%20physical%20copy%20and%20took%20this%20photo.%20The%20shooting%20was%20at%208%3A34pm%20ET%20on%20Saturday%20night.%20Is%20this%20not%20enough%20time%20to%20get%20the%20story%20in%20print%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20news%20outlets%20can%20make%20changes%20to%20their%20print%20editions%20until%20late%20at%20night%2C%20or%20even%20the%20early%20morning%2C%20the%20Times%20said%20in%20an%20X%20post%20responding%20to%20the%20backlash%20that%20its%20Sunday%20print%20edition%20%26quot%3Bgoes%20to%20press%20at%208pm%20Saturday.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20there%20are%20no%20more%20Sunday%20print%20editions%20and%20that%20the%20shooting%20will%20be%20featured%20on%20the%20front%20page%20of%20Monday's%20print%20edition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20print%20edition%20is%20an%20anachronism%20for%20old%20fogies%20like%20me%20who%20still%20like%20newsprint%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20X%20user%20responded%20to%20Maguire.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20want%20the%20latest%20news%2C%20you%20know%20where%20to%20go.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-york-times-print-edition-shooting-coverage-backlash-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777231928000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ee5d3ca98bc8fdc096ef3c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-york-times-print-edition-shooting-coverage-backlash-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20some%20believe%20the%20Times%20intentionally%20didn't%20feature%20the%20shooting%20in%20its%20print%20edition%20on%20Sunday%2C%20the%20reality%20is%20just%20a%20quirk%20of%20newsprint.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lvaranasi%40businessinsider.com%20(Lakshmi%20Varanasi)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Did%20Trump%20save%20eight%20Iranian%20women%20from%20execution%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777231018000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F1b21%2Flive%2F246eea50-4194-11f1-bd52-e755d604ece4.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fcx2e2lg2ny9o%233%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20president%20says%20he%20saved%20eight%20Iranian%20women%20from%20execution%2C%20but%20Iran%20says%20otherwise.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fcx2e2lg2ny9o%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rambling%20hurts%20your%20case%3A%20Immigration%20lawyer%20reveals%20how%20US%20visa%20decisions%20are%20made%20and%20why%20they%20are%20denied%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777230870000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-130538874%2Cimgsize-59164.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesof