l%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20didn't%20like%20that%20my%20son%20was%20spending%20his%20allowance%20on%20gaming%20purchases.%20Turns%20out%2C%20he%20was%20learning%20financial%20responsibility.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223085%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kid%20playing%20videogames%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69d7e933f976785dcb18fe85%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222314%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAt%20first%2C%20in-game%20purchases%20felt%20like%20such%20a%20waste%20of%20money%20to%20me.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELetting%20my%20son%20spend%20his%20money%20was%20an%20effective%20and%20safe%20way%20to%20help%20him%20make%20financial%20decisions.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOpen%20conversation%2C%20rather%20than%20control%2C%20is%20helping%20us%20encourage%20his%20independence.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20first%20stepped%20into%20the%20world%20of%20kid-oriented%20apps%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteenage-girl-moms-debit-card-64000-mobile-games-family-savings-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eonline%20gaming%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20saw%20in-game%20purchases%20as%20nothing%20more%20than%20buying%20%3Cem%3Enothing%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%2011-year-old%20son%20has%20always%20been%20careful%20with%20his%20money%2C%20perhaps%20to%20a%20fault.%20As%20he%20grew%20increasingly%20willing%20to%20spend%20more%20and%20more%20of%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Froblox-accused-in-lawsuit-deleting-in-game-items-without-refunds-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eallowance%20on%20Robux%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20V-bucks%2C%20and%20Minecoins%2C%20we%20were%20alarmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20whole%20thing%20irks%20me.%20I%20really%20struggle%20with%20virtual%20%26quot%3Bcosmetic%26quot%3B%20purchases.%20Buying%20Skins%2C%20special%20emotes%20(expressions%20and%20dance%20moves%2C%20I%20think%3F)%2C%20and%20expensive%20Nikes%20for%20your%20avatar%3F%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20can't%20wrap%20my%20frugal%20mind%20around%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20we%20tried%20to%20steer%20our%20son%20away%20from%20gaming%20purchases.%20We%20talked%20about%20the%20lure%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-deal-with-a-shopping-addiction-2018-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einstant%20gratification%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20impulse%20buying.%20But%20we%20also%20listened%20to%20his%20side%20of%20the%20story.%20And%20we%20realized%20this%20was%20simply%20a%20world%20we%20did%20not%20understand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20our%20son's%20logic%20about%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffish-in-japan-charged-their-owners-credit-card-nintendo-switch-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egaming%20purchases%3C%2Fa%3E%20helped%20us%20hand%20him%20the%20reins%20to%20make%20his%20own%20spending%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225e1b9bbd-991f-4acd-94ad-2375cb6618ae%5C%22%3EGaming%20purchases%20encouraged%20our%20son's%20financial%20responsibility%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20give%20our%20two%20kids%20an%20allowance%20of%20%245%20a%20week.%20Their%20only%20other%20source%20of%20money%20comes%20from%20relatives'%20gifts.%20Our%20main%20purpose%20with%20allowance%20is%20to%20let%20them%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-teach-my-kids-about-money-using-back-school-shopping-2019-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epractice%20spending%20their%20own%20money%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20make%20their%20own%20mistakes%2C%20and%20learn%20how%20they%20want%20to%20interact%20with%20money%20in%20adulthood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222401%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Boy%20holding%20fornite%20card%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69d7f02c96ef6a4c9d1215c2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221801%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author's%2011-year-old%20learned%20financial%20responsibility%20by%20spending%20money%20on%20games.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20our%20son%20is%20tirelessly%20methodical%2C%20our%20younger%20daughter%20lives%20for%20a%20blind%20box.%20As%20with%20everything%20else%2C%20our%20parental%20approach%20to%20their%20spending%20varies%20between%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20few%20years%20of%20making%20his%20own%20spending%20decisions%20under%20his%20belt%2C%20our%20son%20has%20grown%20skeptical%20of%20gimmicky%20offers%20that%20require%20urgency%20and%20any%20deal%20that%20sounds%20too%20good%20to%20be%20true.%20He%20is%20getting%20a%20taste%20of%20the%20real%20world%20in%20the%20digital%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20become%20more%20strategic%20with%20his%20money%2C%20too.%20Fortnite%20recently%20increased%20the%20price%20of%20V-bucks%20%E2%80%94%20its%20in-game%20currency%20%E2%80%94%20so%20our%20son%20asked%20for%20my%20advice%20on%20his%20plan%20to%20stock%20up%20before%20the%20price%20jump.%20I%20told%20him%20that%20is%20exactly%20what%20I%20would%20do%20if%20I%20knew%20the%20price%20of%20something%20I%20love%20was%20about%20to%20go%20up.%20He%20decided%20to%20spend%20a%20little%20more%20than%20he%20normally%20would%2C%20reasoning%20it%20was%20better%20to%20buy%20now%20to%20save%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20we%20don't%20pay%20for%20any%20gaming-related%20purchases%20outside%20Christmas%20or%20birthday%20presents%2C%20our%20son%20also%20budgets%20for%20an%20annual%20%2480%20PlayStation%20Plus%20subscription%2C%20which%20he%20researched%20as%20the%20cheapest%20option.%20It's%20a%20cost%20he%20has%20to%20cover%20to%20do%20what%20matters%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cbc3e597-bbdb-44d4-9967-d3a26433d849%5C%22%3EI%20believe%20these%20in-game%20decisions%20now%20will%20pay%20off%20in%20adulthood.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20stopped%20policing%20our%20son's%20gaming%20purchases%2C%20it%20made%20it%20easier%20to%20have%20open%20conversations%20about%20money.%20He%20is%20proud%20to%20tell%20us%20about%20his%20purchases%20and%20sees%20them%20as%20savvy%20decisions.%20When%20he%20makes%20a%20mistake%2C%20we%20strive%20to%20meet%20him%20with%20respect%20and%20support%2C%20without%20fixing%20it%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Child%20playing%20minecraft%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69d7f054f976785dcb18fee0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222519%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20in%20these%20conversations%20that%20I've%20realized%20that%20gaming%20is%20an%20essential%20part%20of%20our%20son's%20social%20life.%20Most%20of%20his%20purchasing%20decisions%20revolve%20around%20gaming%20with%20friends%20%E2%80%94%20from%20the%20PS5%20subscription%20to%20buying%20the%20latest%20game%20his%20friends%20are%20playing%2C%20and%20even%20gifting%20skins%20or%20Roblox%20items%20to%20friends%20so%20they%20can%20have%20more%20fun%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThinking%20about%20it%20this%20way%2C%20it%20makes%20sense%20that%20he%20would%20rather%20spend%20money%20on%20gaming%20than%20on%20the%20toy%20aisle.%20And%20really%2C%20is%20one%20any%20more%20gimmicky%20than%20the%20other%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20asked%20him%20what%20he%20would%20advise%20other%20parents%20to%20do%20for%20their%20kids%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BRemember%20that%20it's%20not%20just%20silly%20little%20outfits%20or%20superficial%20things.%20Sometimes%20it%20can%20buy%20fun%20experiences.%20So%20if%20they're%20spending%20their%20own%20money%2C%20let%20them%20go%20nuts.%20They'll%20find%20consequences%20sooner%20or%20later.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMuch%20to%20our%20surprise%2C%20in-game%20purchases%20are%20teaching%20our%20son%20that%20spending%20money%20on%20experiences%20with%20others%20%E2%80%94%20even%20virtual%20ones%20%E2%80%94%20is%20often%20more%20worthwhile%20than%20spending%20money%20on%20stuff.%20That's%20a%20value%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20have%20built%20our%20lives%20on%2C%20and%20one%20I'm%20glad%20our%20son%20is%20learning%20on%20his%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkids-in-game-purchases-financial-lessons-parenting-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777226521000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69d7e94d05c9b303c4e76a90%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkids-in-game-purchases-financial-lessons-parenting-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20resisted%20my%20son's%20gaming%20purchases%2C%20but%20they%20ended%20up%20teaching%20him%20budgeting%2C%20planning%2C%20and%20financial%20responsibility.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Katie%20Matthews)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20Modi%20Offers%20Prayers%20At%20Kolkata%20Kali%20Temple%20During%20Roadshow%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22PM%20Modi%20began%20his%20roadshow%20by%20performing%20puja%20at%20the%20temple%20and%20seeking%20blessings%20from%20the%20priest.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777226409000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2026-04%2Fp51t6h0g_pm-modi_625x300_26_April_26.jpg%3Fim%3DFeatureCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-offers-prayers-at-kolkata-kali-temple-during-roadshow-11412803%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22PM%20Modi%20began%20his%20roadshow%20by%20performing%20puja%20at%20the%20temple%20and%20seeking%20blessings%20from%20the%20priest.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-offers-prayers-at-kol