ontent%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223441%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Alexa%20Mellardo%20and%20her%20husband%20in%20their%20kitchen%20mid-renovation%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69dce400899c9d3be050fe90%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223023%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EShortly%20after%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20returned%20from%20our%20honeymoon%2C%20we%20moved%20from%20an%20apartment%20in%20New%20York%20City%20to%20a%20three-bedroom%20house%20in%20Greenwich%2C%20Connecticut.%3Cp%3EAlexa%20Mellardo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20remodeled%20our%20600-square-foot%20kitchen%20into%20an%20open-concept%20space.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20took%20down%20walls%2C%20added%20windows%2C%20and%20replaced%20the%20cabinets%20to%20make%20the%20room%20feel%20lighter.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAfter%20the%20three-month%20renovation%2C%20I%20filled%20the%20room%20with%20bright%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbefore-after-photos-surf-cabin-diy-renovation%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecoastal-inspired%20decor%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20returned%20from%20our%20honeymoon%2C%20we%20moved%20from%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshare-expensive-new-york-city-apartment-with-friends-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20City%20apartment%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20a%20three-bedroom%2C%20two-bathroom%20house%20we%20bought%20in%20Greenwich%2C%20Connecticut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20a%20turnkey%20property%20%E2%80%94%20the%20white%20picket%20fence%20and%20bountiful%20rose%20garden%20I'd%20always%20envisioned%20were%20nowhere%20to%20be%20found%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it%20had%20potential.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20kitchen%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20needed%20extensive%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20writing%20off%20its%20harvest-gold%20linoleum%20floors%2C%20Formica%20countertops%2C%20and%20brown%20cabinets%20that%20looked%20straight%20out%20of%20the%20'80s%2C%20we%20viewed%20the%20dated%20interior%20as%20an%20opportunity%20for%20improvement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20rolled%20up%20our%20sleeves%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistakes-i-made-having-kitchen-renovated-how-to-fix-them-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erenovated%20the%20kitchen%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20ultimately%20transforming%20it%20into%20a%20bright%2C%20coastal-inspired%20room%20at%20the%20center%20of%20our%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20designed%20the%20room%20and%20completed%20the%20demolition%2C%20insulation%2C%20drywall%2C%20and%20trim%20ourselves%20(with%20some%20help%20from%20my%20dad)%20and%20hired%20a%20kitchen%20designer%20to%20install%20new%20cabinets%20and%20a%20countertop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20our%20first%20renovation%20project%2C%20so%20we%20felt%20extremely%20excited%20and%20accomplished%20when%20we%20finished%20and%20admired%20the%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOur%20goal%20was%20to%20turn%20the%20dated%20kitchen%20into%20an%20open-concept%2C%20multipurpose%20room.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Alexa%20Mellardo's%20kitchen%20before%20the%20renovation%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69dce4dedfb2c132adcfcd0f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBefore%20we%20started%20construction%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20put%20together%20a%20budget%20and%20desired%20renovation%20timeline.%3Cp%3EAlexa%20Mellardo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20designed%20the%20space%2C%20we%20knew%20we%20didn't%20want%20it%20to%20have%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-rich-people-never-have-kitchens-luxury-interior-designer-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etraditional%20kitchen%20feel%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20goal%20was%20to%20put%20together%20a%20warm%2C%20inviting%20room%20with%20an%20open%20floor%20plan%20where%20we%20could%20seamlessly%20cook%2C%20eat%2C%20relax%2C%20and%20entertain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20the%20front%20door%20opens%20directly%20into%20the%20room%2C%20it%20sets%20the%20tone%20for%20the%20home%20as%20soon%20as%20we%20walk%20in.%20Every%20detail%20mattered%2C%20and%20we%20had%20to%20carefully%20balance%20both%20aesthetics%20and%20functionality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBefore%20starting%20the%20renovation%2C%20we%20decided%20on%20our%20priorities.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Alexa%20Mellardo%20kitchen%20under%20renovation%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69dceaef4d9d0b2056491f9d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESeveral%20walls%20came%20down%20during%20the%20renovation%20process.%3Cp%3EAlexa%20Mellardo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20get%20an%20idea%20of%20how%20much%20we'd%20spend%20during%20the%20renovation%2C%20we%20listed%20all%20of%20our%20desired%20changes%2C%20from%20our%20must-have%20appliances%20to%20our%20wish%20list%20of%20finishing%20touches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20sights%20were%20set%20on%20a%20white%20cast-iron%20farmhouse%20sink%2C%20a%20high-end%20refrigerator%2C%20a%20custom%20farm%20table%2C%20and%20the%20quietest%20dishwasher%20we%20could%20find.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20the%20project%20required%20more%20than%20just%20filling%20up%20our%20shopping%20cart.%20To%20create%20the%20open%20floor%20plan%20we%20designed%2C%20we%20had%20to%20take%20down%20several%20walls%2C%20including%20one%20that%20was%20load-bearing.%20We%20also%20added%20new%20windows%20and%20glass%20farmhouse%20doors%20to%20bring%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-unconventional-ways-to-use-light-in-home-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emore%20natural%20sunlight%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20the%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20major%20expenses%20to%20plan%20for%20included%20electrical%20work%2C%20plumbing%2C%20insulation%2C%20drywall%2C%20flooring%2C%20kitchen%20cabinetry%2C%20hardware%2C%20countertops%2C%20a%20stove%2C%20and%20eventually%20new%20furniture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaking%20so%20many%20decisions%20at%20once%20felt%20overwhelming%2C%20but%20we%20were%20determined%20to%20keep%20our%20three-month%20timeline%20on%20track%20and%20stick%20to%20our%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20cabinets%20were%20the%20centerpiece%20of%20the%20room.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22cabinetry%20in%20Alexa%20Mellardo's%20kitchen%20in%20greenwich%2C%20connecticut%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69dce524899c9d3be050fe91%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20white%20cabinets%20immediately%20brightened%20the%20room.%3Cp%3EAlexa%20Mellardo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20removed%20the%20dated%20brown%20cabinets%20from%20the%20studs%20and%20swapped%20them%20out%20for%20bright%20white%2C%20Shaker-style%20ones%20with%20honey-bronze%20hardware.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20we%20even%20made%20it%20to%20this%20step%2C%20I'd%20already%20planned%20to%20showcase%20my%20favorite%20Anthropologie%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthrifted-vintage-dishes-worth-money-for-dinner-party-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eplates%20and%20glasses%3C%2Fa%3E%20inside%20a%20few%20glass%20cabinets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhen%20it%20came%20time%20to%20furnish%20and%20decorate%2C%20we%20chose%20multifunctional%20pieces%20with%20a%20coastal-cottage%20aesthetic.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Buffet%20in%20Alexa%20Mellardo's%20new%20home%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69dce5b3899c9d3be050fe98%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20buffet%20has%20plenty%20of%20storage%20and%20doubles%20as%20a%20serving%20surface.%3Cp%3EAlexa%20Mellardo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20construction%20took%20three%20months%2C%20we%20needed%20a%20bit%20more%20time%20to%20get%20the%20space%20ready%20for%20guests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20room%20is%20only%20about%20600%20square%20feet%2C%20so%20we%20had%20to%20be%20intentional%20with%20the%20space%20if%20we%20wanted%20it%20to%20look%20clean%20and%20uncluttered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20wall%20opposite%20the%20cabinets%2C%20we%20installed%20an%20arched%20glass%20buffet.%20It%20provides%20plenty%20of%20storage%20and%20doubles%20as%20a%20surface%20for%20serving%20guests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20furniture%20we%20selected%20is%20all%20light%20in%20color%20and%20extremely%20practical.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Alexa%20Mellardo%20kitchen%20after%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69dcf8d7dfb2c132adcfcd8f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20custom%20table%20fits%20the%20space%20perfectly.%3Cp%3EAlexa%20Mellardo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20a%20traditional%20island%2C%20we%20opted%20for%20a%20custom%20farm%20table%20in%20a%20natural%20beachy%20wood%20finish%20that%20could%20serve%20as%20a%20dining%20surface%20and%20prep%20area.%20On%20top%20of%20it%20sits%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fcharcuterie-board-ideas%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eoversized%20charcuterie%20board%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20practical%20and%20aesthetically%20pleasing%20piece.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20removed%20the%20wood-burning%20fireplace%20and%20opted%20for%20a%20modern%20gas%20unit%2C%20complete%20with%20driftwood%20logs.%20We%20styled%20the%20area%20in%20front%20with%20shiplap%20and%20white%20marble%20tiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20seating%2C%20we%20decided%20on%20a%20cozy%20sectional%2C%20statement%20chair%2C%20and%20plush%20ottoman%20that%20doubles%20as%20a%20coffee%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20finishing%20touches%20really%20brought%20our%20vision%20to%20life.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22flowers%20and%20candle%20on%20buffet%20in%20Alexa%20Mellardo's%20table%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69dcf997dfb2c132adcfcd9b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20always%20have%20a%20scented%20candle%20and%20fresh%20flowers%20in%20the%20room.%3Cp%3EAlexa%20Mellardo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20wide%20farmhouse-style%20trim%20throughout%20the%20space%20and%20around%20the%20windows%20ties%20the%20aesthetic%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20always%20have%20fresh%20flowers%20from%20my%20garden%20in%20a%20vase%20and%20beach-themed%20candles%20on%20my%20arched%20cabinet%20buffet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOnce%20one%20of%20our%20least%20favorite%20rooms%20in%20the%20house%2C%20the%20kitchen%20is%20now%20the%20space%20of%20our%20dreams.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Alexa%20Mellardo%20kitchen%20after%20renovation%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69dce71a899c9d3be050fea0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20were%20thrilled%20with%20the%20finished%20product.%3Cp%3EAlexa%20Mellardo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20charming%2C%20quaint%20main%20room%20is%20everything%20I%20hoped%20it%20would%20be.%20I%20spend%20every%20day%20in%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistakes-open-concept-home-interior-designers-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eopen-concept%20kitchen%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20wouldn't%20have%20it%20any%20other%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20serves%20as%20both%20my%20workspace%20and%20a%20calming%20oasis.%20I%20now%20have%20a%20space%20where%20I%20can%20be%20