influences%20in%20my%20life%2C%20shaping%20everything%20from%20how%20I%20see%20the%20world%20to%20how%20I%20dress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20a%2023-year-old%2C%20I%20admire%20her%20sense%20of%20style.%20Throughout%20her%20life%2C%20she's%20built%20an%20elegant%20wardrobe%20that%20draws%20from%20trends%20without%20necessarily%20following%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%2070%20years%20old%2C%20she%20continues%20to%20inspire%20me.%20Whenever%20I%20open%20my%20wardrobe%20to%20choose%20an%20outfit%2C%20I%20carry%20one%20of%20her%20invaluable%20lessons%20with%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220e592630-9cda-4101-a4df-d6541d3cd257%5C%22%3EOne%20of%20her%20core%20beliefs%20is%20that%20accessories%20should%20add%20to%20an%20outfit%2C%20not%20overwhelm%20it%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hand%20figurine%2C%20sunglasses%2C%20gold%20jewelry%2C%20colorful%20bead%20jewelry%2C%20statement%20rings%20and%20various%20hair%20accessories%20on%20the%20white%20table.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ea5737367066d7c2970316%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHoop%20earrings%20are%20a%20timeless%20staple.%3Cp%3EJelena990%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20accessories%2C%20often%20throwing%20on%20chunky%20jewelry%2C%20layering%20bold%20pieces%2C%20and%20stacking%20belts%20on%20my%20hips.%20Although%20my%20grandmother%20appreciates%20outfit%20embellishments%2C%20she's%20taught%20me%20to%20approach%20them%20with%20intention.%20They%20should%20add%20to%20an%20outfit%2C%20not%20overpower%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20she%20isn't%20afraid%20to%20incorporate%20a%20pop%20of%20color%20%E2%80%94%20as%20long%20as%20it%20matches%20her%20accessories%2C%20from%20her%20bag%20to%20her%20shoes%20to%20her%20belt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe's%20also%20strategic%20about%20her%20jewelry%2C%20choosing%20pieces%20based%20on%20her%20neckline%20and%20hairstyle%20that%20day.%20Her%20go-to%20earrings%3F%20Versatile%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-hoop-earrings%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emedium-sized%20hoops%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20are%20big%20enough%20to%20be%20visible%20under%20a%20range%20of%20hairstyles%20without%20dominating%20a%20look.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20my%20favorite%20everyday%20earrings%20are%20silver%20hoops.%20Every%20time%20I%20put%20them%20on%2C%20I%20feel%20like%20they%20brighten%20me%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20I%20play%20around%20with%20maximalist%2C%20trend-forward%20pieces%2C%20I%20stick%20to%20my%20grandmother's%20rules%20when%20I%20want%20to%20look%20elegant%20and%20timeless.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225455cfb7-fb03-48c0-a5de-22fb1aa3ecb7%5C%22%3EShe%20taught%20me%20that%20walking%20with%20confidence%20can%20upgrade%20an%20outfit%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20grandmother%20has%20always%20told%20me%20that%20picking%20out%20beautiful%20pieces%20is%20just%20the%20first%20step%20in%20putting%20together%20a%20great%20outfit.%20The%20way%20I%20carry%20myself%20when%20I'm%20wearing%20it%20can%20make%20or%20break%20a%20look.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20vivid%20memories%20of%20her%20instructing%20me%20to%20walk%20in%20a%20straight%20line%20with%20my%20shoulders%20back%2C%20stepping%20with%20one%20leg%20in%20front%20of%20the%20other.%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20balancing%20books%20on%20my%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fways-to-be-more-confident-right-now-2019-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewalking%20with%20confidence%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20become%20second%20nature%2C%20whether%20I'm%20wearing%20a%20dress%20and%20heels%20or%20a%20sweatsuit%20and%20sneakers.%20She%20was%20right%3A%20It%20does%20make%20my%20clothes%20look%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20when%20my%20grandmother%20has%20dealt%20with%20health%20issues%20that%20affect%20her%20movements%2C%20she's%20always%20followed%20her%20own%20advice%2C%20walking%20straight%20with%20her%20head%20held%20high%20and%20shoulders%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cf1a833d-1888-4b9f-8ab6-a3b00e0a460b%5C%22%3EHer%20wardrobe%20is%20built%20on%20staple%20pieces%20that%20are%20practical%20and%20make%20her%20feel%20good%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20grandmother%20has%20never%20been%20one%20to%20experiment%20much%20with%20clothes.%20I'm%20hard-pressed%20to%20remember%20a%20time%20when%20she%20wasn't%20wearing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-are-capsule-wardrobes-2015-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esimple%20garments%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20straight%20pants%2C%20sweaters%2C%20tight%20long-sleeve%20T-shirts%2C%20or%20loose%20short-sleeve%20T-shirts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20found%20her%20practical%2C%20elegant%20style%20when%20she%20was%20in%20high%20school%20and%20stayed%20true%20to%20it%20through%20every%20stage%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20gravitates%20toward%20easy-to-wear%20pieces%20that%20move%20with%20her%20and%20fit%20her%20body%20well.%20To%20her%2C%20clothes%20are%20meant%20to%20be%20worn%2C%20so%20they%20have%20to%20look%20%3Cem%3Eand%3C%2Fem%3E%20make%20her%20feel%20good%20in%20order%20to%20secure%20a%20spot%20in%20her%20closet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20I've%20focused%20on%20emulating%20her%20wardrobe.%20Every%20item%20I%20buy%20has%20to%20look%20good%2C%20feel%20nice%20on%20my%20body%2C%20and%20be%20practical.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22350a19d6-44f4-4af0-b642-156b30b564ca%5C%22%3EWhen%20she%20layers%2C%20she%20makes%20sure%20the%20pieces%20complement%20each%20other%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224010%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22woman%20walking%20on%20city%20street%20in%20neutral%20clothing%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69dfb36f55edb86c69eccca6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222673%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20grandmother%20taught%20me%20to%20layer%20strategically.%3Cp%3EAnnaZhuk%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20grandmother%20has%20taught%20me%20that%20layering%20well%20requires%20more%20than%20throwing%20on%20multiple%20garments%20and%20calling%20it%20a%20day.%20The%20pieces%20have%20to%20be%20harmonious.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20a%20way%20of%20looking%20elegant%20even%20as%20she%20combines%20unlikely%20pieces.%20When%20she's%20cold%2C%20I%20see%20her%20drape%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-winter-dress-coats-for-women%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elong%20wool%20coat%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20her%20shoulders%2C%20throw%20on%20a%20pair%20of%20leather%20gloves%2C%20and%20tie%20a%20silk%20scarf%20around%20her%20neck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20base%20is%20always%20simple%20and%20cohesive%2C%20creating%20the%20perfect%20foundation%20for%20a%20layered%20outfit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20never%20been%20a%20big%20fan%20of%20layering%20clothes%2C%20but%20I%20use%20the%20same%20approach%20when%20choosing%20accessories.%20I%20start%20with%20a%20plain%20base%20layer%20before%20adding%20small%2C%20complementary%20pieces.%20I%20put%20thought%20into%20each%20one%20and%20consider%20how%20it%20works%20with%20the%20overall%20look.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a4f27698-52b3-4d5f-8039-479c2a2f786a%5C%22%3EMy%20grandmother%20knows%20that%20wrinkles%20can%20ruin%20even%20the%20most%20stylish%20outfit%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%2C%20my%20mom%20often%20insisted%20that%20I%20iron%20my%20clothes%20%E2%80%94%20later%2C%20I%20learned%20that%20the%20advice%20stemmed%20from%20my%20grandmother%2C%20who%20often%20shared%20it%20with%20her%20when%20she%20was%20young.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20all%2C%20even%20the%20best%20outfit%20can%20look%20messy%20if%20it's%20wrinkled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20family%2C%20crisp%20lines%20and%20smooth%20sleeves%20symbolize%20self-respect%20and%20elegance.%20Now%2C%20I%20follow%20their%20advice%20and%20never%20leave%20the%20house%20without%20ironing%20my%20clo