%20how%20well%20the%20broom%20gathered%20human%20hair%20and%20lint%20on%20the%20floor%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221666%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22on%20left%2C%20gray%20carpeting%20with%20pet%20hair%20embedded%3B%20on%20right%2C%20clean%20gray%20carpeting%20cleaned%20of%20hair%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61324e5961f7d80018f22f21%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221249%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOn%20the%20left%2C%20the%20carpet%20before%20I%20raked%20the%20Furemover%20over%20it.%20On%20the%20right%2C%20landlord-approved%20carpet%20free%20of%20hair.%3Cp%3EAnna%20Popp%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20clean%20the%20broom%20after%20use%2C%20I%20followed%20the%20manufacturer's%20instructions%20to%20wash%20the%20head%20under%20the%20faucet%20with%20water%20and%20soap.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225ddfac4f-fe32-4362-b558-c0340f7f2235%5C%22%3EWhat%20makes%20this%20pet%20hair%20broom%20stand%20out%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20recent%20college%20graduate%2C%20it%20suffices%20to%20say%20that%20spending%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20isn't%20always%20doable.%20For%20%2412%2C%20this%20pet%20hair%20broom%20is%20not%20only%20the%20cheapest%20way%20to%20clean%20pet%20hair%20from%20carpets%20but%20it's%20also%20incredibly%20efficient%20and%20easy%20to%20use%20and%20store%20in%20a%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20low%20price%2C%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20the%20broom%20is%20unmatched.%20It%20dislodged%20months%20of%20human%20and%20pet%20hair%2C%20as%20well%20as%20lint%2C%20crumbs%2C%20and%20dust.%20After%20I%20used%20the%20broom%2C%20I%20did%20a%20quick%20vacuum%20and%20realized%20how%20quickly%20my%20inexpensive%20Amazon%20vacuum%20lifted%20anything%20left%20in%20the%20carpets%20thanks%20to%20the%20initial%20cleaning%20with%20the%20broom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221666%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22on%20left%2C%20furemover%20broom%20and%20pile%20of%20collected%20fur%20and%20human%20hair%3B%20on%20right%2C%20a%20closeup%20of%20the%20furemovers%20rubber%20bristles%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61324e3861f7d80018f22f0b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221249%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Furemover%20collects%20a%20lot%20of%20hair%20%E2%80%94%20from%20both%20pets%20and%20humans%20%E2%80%94%20with%20its%20simple%20rubber%20brush%20head.%3Cp%3EAnna%20Popp%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20now%20use%20the%20pet%20hair%20broom%20every%20few%20days%20to%20do%20a%20quick%20comb%20of%20the%20floors%20and%20couches%20for%20pet%20hair.%20Plus%2C%20I%20just%20received%20my%20security%20deposit%20back%20from%20my%20rental%20and%20there%20were%20no%20notes%20about%20pet%20hair%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20this%20broom%20really%20did%20the%20trick.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2236029f12-6771-4fe7-a5f2-77b21262afa3%5C%22%3EThe%20cons%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Furemover%20worked%20wonders%20for%20me%2C%20it's%20not%20a%20vacuum%20cleaner.%20The%20broom%20requires%20light%20manual%20labor%20to%20clean%20carpets%2C%20so%20if%20you%20prefer%20the%20ease%20of%20a%20vacuum%20and%20can%20afford%20one%20that%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-pet-vacuum%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epet%20vacuum%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20that%20could%20be%20a%20better%20option.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20my%20long-haired%20mix%20has%20medium%20to%20long%20fur%20and%20the%20broom%20got%20her%20fur%20out%20of%20the%20carpet%20easily.%20However%2C%20if%20you%20have%20a%20pet%20with%20shorter%20hair%2C%20the%20bristles%20may%20not%20catch%20smaller%20hairs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222434a454-8d13-4753-b89a-0bfab431a2d5%5C%22%3EThe%20bottom%20line%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Furemover%20pet%20hair%20broom%20is%20the%20ultimate%20tool%20for%20removing%20hair%20from%20floors%20and%20it%20aids%20in%20general%20cleaning