ons%20are%20underway%20to%20support%20people%20affected%20by%20the%20Punjab%20floods.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20one%20had%20the%20answers.%20Harmeet%20Singh%2C%20who%20leads%20CSR%20(Corporate%20Social%20Responsibility)%20at%20Kalgidhar%20Trust%2C%20admits%20that%2C%20despite%20having%20conducted%20relief%20and%20rescue%20operations%20for%20the%20last%20two%20decades%2C%20they%20are%20daunted%20by%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20calamity%20%E2%80%94%20these%20are%20being%20called%20the%20worst%20floods%20that%20the%20city%20has%20experienced%20since%201988.%20As%20of%202%3A30%20PM%20on%205%20September%202025%2C%20the%20death%20toll%20stands%20at%2043%2C%20with%201%2C48%2C000%20hectares%20of%20agricultural%20land%20submerged%20under%20water%20and%20with%20it%2C%20thousands%20of%20dreams.%20Punjab%20is%20the%20seat%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20agrarian%20economy%2C%20and%20a%20calamity%20of%20this%20scale%20will%20ripple%20into%20effects%20that%20are%20felt%20across%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20will%20take%20time%20to%20bring%20the%20situation%20under%20control%2C%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20joining%20hands%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EDonatekart%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20to%20help.%20And%20you%20can%20join%20us%20too%2C%20by%20donating%20to%20this%20fundraiser.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.donatekart.com%2FDisaster-Relief%2FThe-Better-India%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Clabel%3EDONATE%20NOW%20%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHelp%20the%20people%20of%20Punjab%3A%20What%20can%20you%20do%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.donatekart.com%2FDisaster-Relief%2FThe-Better-India%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EClick%20on%2